      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Sharpening Amber Fangs",
        "Client": "Waiting Woman",
        "Description": "My boyfriend\u0027s on his way here for my\r\nbirthday. Oh, thank you! Anyway, he\u0027ll\r\nbe passing through the Frost Islands to\r\nget here and I just heard that a Barioth\r\nhas been spotted! Hunter, I didn\u0027t get all\r\ndolled up for nothing! You gotta get rid of\r\nit so he (and his presents) arrive safely!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Barioth",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Crocs d\u0027ambre aiguis\u00E9s",
        "Client": "Femme qui attend",
        "Description": "Mon petit ami vient me voir pour\r\nmon anniversaire, et il doit passer\r\npar l\u0027Archipel de glace. Il para\u00EEt\r\nqu\u0027un Barioth y a \u00E9t\u00E9 aper\u00E7u. Si je\r\nme suis mise sur mon 31, ce n\u0027est\r\npas pour rien, alors je compte sur\r\ntoi pour l\u0027aider \u00E0 arriver ici !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Barioth",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Affilare le zanne",
        "Client": "Donna in ansia",
        "Description": "Il mio fidanzato sta venendo a\r\ntrovarmi per il compleanno.\r\nOh, grazie! Passer\u00E0 per le\r\nIsole ghiacciate, ma hanno\r\navvistato un Barioth laggi\u00F9.\r\nCaccialo, cos\u00EC lui e i regali\r\narriveranno sani e salvi!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Barioth",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Spitze Bernsteinf\u00E4nge",
        "Client": "Wartende Frau",
        "Description": "Mein Freund kommt mich zu meinem\r\nGeburtstag besuchen. Oh, danke! Jeden-\r\nfalls kommt er \u00FCber die Frostinseln her\r\nund ich hab gerade geh\u00F6rt, dass da ein\r\nBarioth gesehen wurde! H\u00F6r zu, ich hab\r\nmich nicht umsonst so aufgedonnert!\r\nSorg daf\u00FCr, dass er sicher ankommt!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Barioth.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Afilando colmillos de \u00E1mbar",
        "Client": "Mujer a la espera",
        "Description": "\u00A1Por favor, ayuda!\r\nMi novio viene a verme por\r\nmi cumplea\u00F1os, pero pasar\u00E1\r\npor las Islas heladas, donde\r\nse ha visto un Barioth hace\r\npoco. \u00A1Podr\u00EDa correr un gran\r\npeligro!",
